{
  "video_id": "4Z_IRkfBlEA",
  "title": "An Ice Castle Brings Magic Before Melting Away",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 9170.0,
      "end_time": 11107.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] Castles are built to last, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 11107.0,
      "end_time": 14329.0,
      "text": "One hundred years, 500 years, a thousand years."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14330.0,
      "end_time": 18600.0,
      "text": "So why build a castle that only exists for three months"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18600.0,
      "end_time": 21143.0,
      "text": "and has to be rebuilt every single year when it melts?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22400.0,
      "end_time": 24343.0,
      "text": "Well, what if that was the point?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25233.0,
      "end_time": 28440.0,
      "text": "What if you were building it not for the finished product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28440.0,
      "end_time": 29889.0,
      "text": "but just 'cause you like building stuff?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29889.0,
      "end_time": 32300.0,
      "text": "(chainsaw buzzing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32299.999999999996,
      "end_time": 33730.0,
      "text": "- We're just creating for fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33730.0,
      "end_time": 35750.0,
      "text": "creating something that's going to melt."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35750.0,
      "end_time": 37150.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] And because you want to make something"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37150.0,
      "end_time": 39400.0,
      "text": "that looks like it belongs in a fairy tale."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39400.0,
      "end_time": 40600.0,
      "text": "- I'm Sleeping Beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40600.0,
      "end_time": 41220.0,
      "text": "It's nice to meet you."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41220.0,
      "end_time": 43960.0,
      "text": "- I was just blown when I saw it."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43960.0,
      "end_time": 44890.0,
      "text": "- Blown away."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 44890.0,
      "end_time": 47100.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] Even if it can't last forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47100.0,
      "end_time": 49547.0,
      "text": "But then, the best things in life never do."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 49547.0,
      "end_time": 52629.0,
      "text": "(excavator rumbling)"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58350.0,
      "end_time": 60810.0,
      "text": "So in what faraway land of ice and snow"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60810.0,
      "end_time": 62790.0,
      "text": "might you find this unique castle?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 62790.0,
      "end_time": 64641.0,
      "text": "Tell me at what state to be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64641.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67213.0,
      "text": "- America. - New Hampshire."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 67213.0,
      "end_time": 69270.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] This is the aptly-named White Mountains"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 69270.0,
      "end_time": 70630.0,
      "text": "National Forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70630.0,
      "end_time": 72580.0,
      "text": "Now, there's no doubt that this is one of the most"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 72580.0,
      "end_time": 74429.0,
      "text": "beautiful parts of the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 74430.0,
      "end_time": 77290.0,
      "text": "But people who don't like the cold tend to stay away"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 77290.0,
      "end_time": 78900.0,
      "text": "because temperatures here have been known"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 78900.0,
      "end_time": 81830.0,
      "text": "to fall as low as minus 100 degrees Fahrenheit"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81830.0,
      "end_time": 82740.0,
      "text": "with wind chill."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 82740.0,
      "end_time": 85643.0,
      "text": "Yes, minus 100 degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 87470.0,
      "end_time": 90940.0,
      "text": "- We have trees, and we have a lot of land,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 90940.0,
      "end_time": 93471.0,
      "text": "and we have the Ice Castles."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 93471.0,
      "end_time": 96780.0,
      "text": "(ethereal music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 96780.0,
      "end_time": 98100.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] For the last four winters"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98100.0,
      "end_time": 100300.0,
      "text": "this hidden corner of New England has been home"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100300.0,
      "end_time": 102880.0,
      "text": "to the Ice Castle, a gargantuan structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 102880.0,
      "end_time": 106850.0,
      "text": "made up of over 25 million pounds of ice."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106850.0,
      "end_time": 109330.0,
      "text": "Thousands of visitors come to explore the turrets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 109330.0,
      "end_time": 111390.0,
      "text": "tunnels, slides, and sculptures that seem"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 111390.0,
      "end_time": 113730.0,
      "text": "to have sprung out of the ground like magic."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 113730.0,
      "end_time": 116858.0,
      "text": "- They have really fun slides with lights in them."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 116858.0,
      "end_time": 118941.0,
      "text": "- I'm ready for anything!"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 120865.0,
      "end_time": 123592.0,
      "text": "- And a fire-breathing princess."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 124719.0,
      "end_time": 128366.0,
      "text": "(screaming, exclaiming)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 128366.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130100.00000000001,
      "text": "(whooshing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 130100.0,
      "end_time": 132301.0,
      "text": "- I was scared she was gonna blow up the whole thing down."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 132301.0,
      "end_time": 135700.0,
      "text": "Then we call the fire department, and then something bad"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 135700.0,
      "end_time": 138313.0,
      "text": "would happen, and maybe she would get arrested."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140650.0,
      "end_time": 143500.0,
      "text": "- Arabelle and Lily are best friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 143500.0,
      "end_time": 145630.0,
      "text": "or worst enemies, depending on the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 145630.0,
      "end_time": 148320.0,
      "text": "Arabelle completely looks up to Liliana."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 148320.0,
      "end_time": 150893.0,
      "text": "I think she wants to be like Lily one day."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150893.0,
      "end_time": 152290.0,
      "text": "- Come on!"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 152290.0,
      "end_time": 153448.0,
      "text": "Whoa!"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 153448.0,
      "end_time": 155474.0,
      "text": "Why do I keep on slipping?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 155474.0,
      "end_time": 157250.0,
      "text": "(shrieking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 157251.0,
      "end_time": 158757.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] How did you feel when you first"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 158757.0,
      "end_time": 160490.0,
      "text": "saw the Ice Castle?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 160490.0,
      "end_time": 162300.0,
      "text": "- I felt amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 162300.0,
      "end_time": 166410.0,
      "text": "- I felt like how did they build this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 166410.0,
      "end_time": 168233.0,
      "text": "It could be all magic."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 170753.0,
      "end_time": 174149.0,
      "text": "- Um, they might have done magic, I don't know."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 175500.0,
      "end_time": 178457.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] The Ice Castle is, in fact, built with magic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 178457.0,
      "end_time": 180930.0,
      "text": "but it's the kind of magic that results from a group"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 180930.0,
      "end_time": 183713.0,
      "text": "of craftspeople working in subfreezing temperatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 183713.0,
      "end_time": 185970.0,
      "text": "for a cumulative 8,000 hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 185970.0,
      "end_time": 188440.0,
      "text": "(chainsaw buzzing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 188440.0,
      "end_time": 190550.0,
      "text": "- We actually harvest our own icicles here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 190550.0,
      "end_time": 192210.0,
      "text": "and then we take them and stick them"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192210.0,
      "end_time": 194400.0,
      "text": "where we want the ice to grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 194400.0,
      "end_time": 196240.0,
      "text": "And then we turn on the sprinkler system"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 196240.0,
      "end_time": 198540.0,
      "text": "and overnight it'll grow together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 198540.0,
      "end_time": 199940.0,
      "text": "and once it grows together it's strong enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 199940.0,
      "end_time": 202650.0,
      "text": "to get up on top, and we keep building from there."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 202650.0,
      "end_time": 203707.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] And there's another group of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 203707.0,
      "end_time": 206840.0,
      "text": "who help shape the castle without even knowing it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 206840.0,
      "end_time": 208200.0,
      "text": "the visitors themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 208200.0,
      "end_time": 210440.0,
      "text": "- I like for people to touch it, and get in it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 210440.0,
      "end_time": 213250.0,
      "text": "and see them interacting with the ice."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 213250.0,
      "end_time": 214830.0,
      "text": "They're essentially helping me carve"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 214830.0,
      "end_time": 217500.0,
      "text": "because the heat from people's mittens and bottoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 217500.0,
      "end_time": 220490.0,
      "text": "will continue to carve the castle and smooth it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 220490.0,
      "end_time": 222360.0,
      "text": "I'm gonna try to knock off this part."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 222360.0,
      "end_time": 223470.0,
      "text": "- Is it fun?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 223470.0,
      "end_time": 224950.0,
      "text": "- [Woman] Yeah, it is fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 224950.0,
      "end_time": 225987.0,
      "text": "- Is it like all year? - It's really fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 225987.0,
      "end_time": 230987.0,
      "text": "No, no, we start building in December, usually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 231410.0,
      "end_time": 232820.0,
      "text": "when it gets cold enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 232820.0,
      "end_time": 236160.0,
      "text": "I think you have to be 18, but you just apply online."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 236160.0,
      "end_time": 238100.0,
      "text": "I really like telling children how it's made."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 238100.0,
      "end_time": 240880.0,
      "text": "I'm like, this is the next generation of artists."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 240880.0,
      "end_time": 244000.0,
      "text": "I like to work with happy accidents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 244000.0,
      "end_time": 245630.0,
      "text": "and ice is great because you don't"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 245630.0,
      "end_time": 247790.0,
      "text": "have a lot of control over it."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 247800.0,
      "end_time": 250470.0,
      "text": "It's all up to the weather, and it changes all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 250470.0,
      "end_time": 252840.0,
      "text": "New Hampshire, it's a tough place to live"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 252840.0,
      "end_time": 255420.0,
      "text": "because you have to be able to handle the winters."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 255420.0,
      "end_time": 256959.0,
      "text": "I think everyone's a little stir-crazy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 256959.0,
      "end_time": 258990.0,
      "text": "and you just don't know what to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 258100.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259650.00000000003,
      "text": "when you're trapped in your house all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 259649.0,
      "end_time": 261253.0,
      "text": "and especially if you have kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 262180.0,
      "end_time": 263990.0,
      "text": "I feel like art could help to make connections"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 263990.0,
      "end_time": 265200.0,
      "text": "and work through things."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 265200.0,
      "end_time": 266966.0,
      "text": "- How do you spell sadness?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 266966.0,
      "end_time": 268640.0,
      "text": "- S-A-D-N."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 268640.0,
      "end_time": 270810.0,
      "text": "- Art is a great way to work through problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 270810.0,
      "end_time": 274900.0,
      "text": "and emotions, and putting emotions into something."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 274900.0,
      "end_time": 274923.0,
      "text": "- Is that you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 274923.0,
      "end_time": 275756.0,
      "text": "- Mm hmm."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 277690.0,
      "end_time": 280900.0,
      "text": "- I feel for my children because for most of their life"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 280900.0,
      "end_time": 285490.0,
      "text": "it was almost picture-perfect, and then it went from"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 285500.0,
      "end_time": 287220.0,
      "text": "perfect to crumbling really fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 287220.0,
      "end_time": 288224.0,
      "text": "- Ow, wow."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 288224.0,
      "end_time": 289400.0,
      "text": "- [Woman] Whoa, okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 289400.0,
      "end_time": 293823.0,
      "text": "- Well, my mom and my dad got in a divorce."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 296330.0,
      "end_time": 300900.0,
      "text": "Sometimes stuff is just for the best,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 300900.0,
      "end_time": 305900.0,
      "text": "and sometimes that's just gonna happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 305244.0,
      "end_time": 307744.0,
      "text": "(quiet music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 308883.0,
      "end_time": 312370.0,
      "text": "- Christmas wasn't like all the Christmases before."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 312370.0,
      "end_time": 316890.0,
      "text": "So we went to the Ice Castles, and I think it was"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 316890.0,
      "end_time": 318780.0,
      "text": "just the pick-me-up we all kinda needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 318780.0,
      "end_time": 323920.0,
      "text": "It was a day away from reality, and it was magical."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 323930.0,
      "end_time": 326910.0,
      "text": "Maybe it's not a bad thing that they're experiencing"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 326910.0,
      "end_time": 330950.0,
      "text": "heartbreak so early on because they're learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 330950.0,
      "end_time": 333370.0,
      "text": "that there is life after heartbreak."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 333370.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "You can go through something and you can be"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 337430.0,
      "text": "in a lot of pain, and you can get through it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 337430.0,
      "end_time": 339173.0,
      "text": "and you can come out stronger."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 340830.0,
      "end_time": 344530.0,
      "text": "- If Arabelle's sad, I would give her a hug,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 344530.0,
      "end_time": 347429.0,
      "text": "and say, just try to think of the good times you had,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 347430.0,
      "end_time": 350530.0,
      "text": "or the good times that you will have."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 354290.0,
      "end_time": 355920.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] All good things come to an end."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 355920.0,
      "end_time": 357290.0,
      "text": "Maybe that's what helps us realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 357290.0,
      "end_time": 358590.0,
      "text": "that they are good things."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 359840.0,
      "end_time": 361119.0,
      "text": "And besides, who knows?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 361120.0,
      "end_time": 363360.0,
      "text": "Something even better might be around the corner."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 363360.0,
      "end_time": 364820.0,
      "text": "- I'm happy to see it melt."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 364820.0,
      "end_time": 366800.0,
      "text": "It needs to be renewed."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 366800.0,
      "end_time": 367130.0,
      "text": "It needs to melt."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 367990.0,
      "end_time": 369950.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] Sometimes, though, mother nature needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 369950.0,
      "end_time": 371490.0,
      "text": "a little bit of help."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 371490.0,
      "end_time": 374407.0,
      "text": "(excavator beeping)"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 374407.0,
      "end_time": 376100.0,
      "text": "(ice crumbling)"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 376100.0,
      "end_time": 378960.0,
      "text": "The Ice Castle is so big, that even when temperatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 378960.0,
      "end_time": 381320.0,
      "text": "get above freezing it has to be knocked down"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 381321.0,
      "end_time": 384540.0,
      "text": "because it takes too long to melt."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 384540.0,
      "end_time": 385860.0,
      "text": "- I definitely embrace change."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 385860.0,
      "end_time": 387780.0,
      "text": "Dive into a season, and then as soon as you're sick"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 387780.0,
      "end_time": 389200.0,
      "text": "of that season, that season's gone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 389200.0,
      "end_time": 391700.0,
      "text": "and there's a new season."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 391700.0,
      "end_time": 393349.0,
      "text": "When spring comes, I start to garden."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 393350.0,
      "end_time": 395600.0,
      "text": "Soon as the drips of the Ice Castles start happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 395600.0,
      "end_time": 397730.0,
      "text": "I was like, OK, let's have some springtime."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 397730.0,
      "end_time": 399590.0,
      "text": "I want to see plants burst out of the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 399590.0,
      "end_time": 400852.0,
      "text": "and I want to tackle them."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 400853.0,
      "end_time": 403603.0,
      "text": "(cheerful music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 404540.0,
      "end_time": 406482.0,
      "text": "- [Marc] Are you excited to go back next year?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 406482.0,
      "end_time": 408000.0,
      "text": "- [Together] Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 408000.0,
      "end_time": 411550.0,
      "text": "- I'm so excited because maybe there will be"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 411550.0,
      "end_time": 416550.0,
      "text": "another fire-breathing princess, and the slides"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 416630.0,
      "end_time": 418573.0,
      "text": "hopefully will still be there."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 420410.0,
      "end_time": 423393.0,
      "text": "And maybe there'll be a little change."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 423393.0,
      "end_time": 424226.0,
      "text": "Mm hmm."
    }
  ]
}